milestones.description: Allan Donald has taken the most five-wicket hauls (2) in ODIs for SA, going past Richard Snell's record
Hansie Cronje and Jonty Rhodes's 101-run partnership is SA's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 92 between McMillan and Gary Kirsten
South Africa's 203-run win against Kenya is the largest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 169-run win against U.A.E.
Chudasama has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (9) for KENYA, going past Aasif Karim
Otieno has broken the record for most dismissals (3) in ODIs for KENYA, going past Tariq Iqbal's 2
